name: Mixed Strand Bracelet
description:
A bracelet made from three strands including a brass ball chain, a navy blue embroidery rope, and a faux leather band. Adorned with a brass washer, and a diamond charm at the end of a chain.

One size fits most, but if you have a larger/smaller wrist, please contact me first and I'll gladly accomodate.

name: Friendship Bracelet for Adults
description:
Loom woven embroidery thread in a flower pattern with a chain and diamond-shaped charm. Uses a Lobster Claw Clasp for closure.

Because each bracelet is made from scratch, it may take up to 1-2 weeks  depending on demand. The weaving process takes some time. Contact me if you have questions on how long your bracelet will take!

One size fits most, but if you have a larger/smaller wrist, please contact me first and I'll gladly accomodate.

description:

Great for stacking with other bracelets, or worn on its own.
